Used in the {icon:Icon_Tooltip_Marker_Dungeon_BossSummon,1.8} {c_highlight}Hanged Man's Hall{/c} in {c_important}Kehjistan{/c} with {icon:Icon_Tooltip_MiscTrinkets_VoodooDoll_001,2} {c_pickups}Pincushioned Doll{/c} to summon a powerful enemy. Requires {c_number}2{/c}. 

Acquired from {icon:Icon_Tooltip_Marker_Boss,1.5} {c_highlight}Lord Zir{/c} within {icon:Icon_Tooltip_Marker_WargroundWaypoint,1.8} {c_highlight}The Darkened Way{/c} in {c_important}Fractured Peaks{/c} in {c_important}Torment difficulties{/c} only by the one who performs the summoning. 

Rarely found from {icon:Icon_Tooltip_Marker_WorldEvent,1.5} {c_highlight}World Bosses{/c}
